<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Takanashi Kiara - HoloCure Character</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .character-profile {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: start;
            padding: 2rem;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        .character-image {
            max-width: 300px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .character-info {
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .stats-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .stats-table th, .stats-table td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .stats-table th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .weapon-section {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .weapon-image {
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <main>
        <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">Takanashi Kiara</h1>

        <div class="character-profile">
            <img src="/images/kiara.jpg" alt="Takanashi Kiara" class="character-image">
            <div class="character-info">
                <h2>Background</h2>
                <p>Takanashi Kiara is a phoenix, an immortal bird that rises from its own ashes. She's also the manager of a fast-food restaurant chain. With her fiery personality and endless enthusiasm, Kiara brings warmth and energy to any situation.</p>

                <h2>Stats</h2>
                <table class="stats-table">
                    <tr>
                        <th>Stat</th>
                        <th>Value</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>HP</td>
                        <td>110</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>ATK</td>
                        <td>1.15x</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>SPD</td>
                        <td>1.30x</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>CRT</td>
                        <td>4%</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <div class="weapon-section">
                    <h2>Weapon: Phoenix Sword</h2>
                    <img src="/images/weapons/phoenix_sword.png" alt="Phoenix Sword" class="weapon-image">
                    <p>Kiara's primary weapon is her Phoenix Sword, a magical blade infused with the power of rebirth. This versatile weapon can transform into a shield for defense.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Damage: High</li>
                        <li>Range: Medium</li>
                        <li>Special Effect: Can transform into a shield, granting temporary invincibility</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

    <script type="module">
        // Your Firebase configuration and initialization code here
    </script>
</body>
</html>
